{"tid":1683903,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"比利時禁止孔子學院院長宋新寧入境","createTime":"2019-10-31T00:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T00:52:14.000Z","uid":9049,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fe98723439c3e05f48485a3f7f7529b947d7460e","tid":1683903,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T00:23:01.000Z","msg":"比利時禁止孔子學院院長宋新寧入境<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=368161&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D368161%26refer%3DShare&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHj2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=babfd072\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D368161%26refer%3DShare&h=bf8ea0e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=368161&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】比利時以國家安全為理由，禁止比利時荷語自由大學孔子學院院長宋新寧入境。 <br />\n<br />\n比利時內政部證實，入境部門今年九月初拒絕向中國政治學家宋新寧發出入境許可證，禁止他入境八年，有關措施同時會在歐盟神根公約26個成員國生效，不過內政部以私隱為理由拒絕披露更多詳情。<br />\n<br />\n當地傳媒報道，比利時情報部門去年向荷語自由大學發出警告，指有人企圖透過孔子學院為中國從事間諜活動，危害比利時國家安全，宋新寧否認指控，並就比利時的決定提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n位於布魯塞爾的荷語自由大學在2016年成立孔子學院，由在比利時活躍多年的宋新寧擔任院長。當地傳媒報道指，宋新寧利用在當地的人脈關係，向學術界及有影響力的人士散播對中國有利的言論及立場，並發展出一個情報網絡，招募中國留學生及商人充當線人。"},{"pid":"c9ec6a6e2bcd7ee71419f97ede1becef718e3709","tid":1683903,"uid":41524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T00:23:47.000Z","msg":"哎呀"},{"pid":"eb48cc0f7136db009b927758fc07edfe1007291a","tid":1683903,"uid":69646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T00:24:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22b0214d5cc0788d28af10c4526512451288c133","tid":1683903,"uid":8562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T00:46:39.000Z","msg":"收埋間咩學院皮啦"},{"pid":"4dea9ab4e1a709dff7c1e77904b2e99ad83e7b1a","tid":1683903,"uid":137506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T00:50:33.000Z","msg":"孔子學院喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支諜就支諜啦"},{"pid":"cc31a3a113005bd922617058978e17cd3738bef2","tid":1683903,"uid":40763,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T00:52:14.000Z","msg":"我諗孔子都估唔到係現代自己會做左間諜icon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}